OL,4,C'Our flight refund battle for mum who
OL,5,Ccan barely walk'
OL,6, An elderly grandmother who can "barely
OL,7, walk" has finally been sent a refund -
OL,8, a year after her flight was cancelled.
OL,10,FVeronica Brown, aged 85, had hoped to
OL,11,Fvisit her son and grandchildren in
OL,12,FMunich last Easter, until Covid
OL,13,Frestrictions put an end to her plans.
OL,15,FHer daughter Clare D'Agostino said,
OL,16,Fwith little prospect of rearranging,
OL,17,Fthere was "no way on earth" they would
OL,18,Fhave chosen a voucher over a refund.
OL,20,FBut they were sent one anyway, until
OL,21,Fthe BBC followed up the case.
